    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ABOUT THE EXPERIENCE:</h2><br><i><strong>Insomnia</strong>: &quot;prolonged and usually abnormal inability to get enough sleep especially due to trouble falling asleep or staying asleep&quot; - Some Dictionary</i><br><br><strong>The game is simple... Try to sleep.</strong> We can't promise that the night will be uneventful, however. Between apparitions of ancient interdimensional entities to a city that never sleeps, overcoming your insomnia may prove to be difficult.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EARLY ACCESS FEATURES:</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A cozy bed to sleep in,<br></li><li>An elegant but unreliable pocket watch subject to the wills of the supernatural,<br></li><li>Retro alarm clock to keep track of the countless hours you haven't slept,<br></li><li>Immersive sound design made by a schizophrenic insomniac,<br></li><li><i>Your own personal sleep paralysis demon!</i></li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2148240/extras/a255bc67311c941eb64c0ac4cbc7d87f.poster.avif?t=1668132453\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2148240/extras/a255bc67311c941eb64c0ac4cbc7d87f.webm?t=1668132453\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2148240/extras/a255bc67311c941eb64c0ac4cbc7d87f.mp4?t=1668132453\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >RELEASE ROADMAP:</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>More dreamscapes to explore and interact with,<br></li><li>Additional spontaneous events to experience in the waking world,<br></li><li>New decisions to make and additional endings to discover,<br></li><li>Comprehensive conclusion to the story and the hints that correlate,</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2148240/extras/41695e2730ec7331b3ba09d0482b6fbe.poster.avif?t=1668132453\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2148240/extras/41695e2730ec7331b3ba09d0482b6fbe.webm?t=1668132453\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2148240/extras/41695e2730ec7331b3ba09d0482b6fbe.mp4?t=1668132453\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
